Comprehensive Method Reference
Category	Method	Description
Adding	add(E e)	Appends the element to the end of the list.
	add(int index, E e)	Inserts the element at the specified position.
	addAll(Collection c)	Appends all elements of a collection to the end.
Accessing	get(int index)	Returns the element at the specified index.
	indexOf(Object o)	Returns the first occurrence index of the element; -1 if not found.
	lastIndexOf(Object o)	Returns the last occurrence index of the element.
Updating	set(int index, E e)	Replaces the element at the index with the new element.
