	isEmpty()	Returns true if the list contains no elements.
	size()	Returns the number of elements in the list.
Iterating	iterator()	Returns an iterator over the elements in proper sequence.
	listIterator()	Returns a list iterator (allows bi-directional traversal).
Utility	sort(Comparator c)	Sorts the list based on the provided comparator.
	toArray()	Converts the ArrayList into a standard Array.
